comments.body:
Thanks [~sunilg], 

Overall looks good, except: 
{code:java}
266	if (container.isContainerInFinalStates()) {
267	releasingGpus++;
268	}{code}
Instead of ++, you should add the actual # of allocated GPUs of the container. 

And even if the patch looks safe, could u add a test to make sure there's no regression in the future?
